Author: Alt.Estate
Title: [ANN] Alt.Estate — Trade Tokenized Real Estate! USA, Japan, EU... [BOUNTYHIVE]
Body: Different people will benefit from buying property tokens on our platform: institutional investors, crypto traders, owners of cryptocurrencies, middle class and crypto whales.  💳 Crypto Investors Crypto investors gain easy access to new assets. It is impossible to know precisely how many people use cryptocurrency but all the studies show that there are millions of unique active users and the number is expected to grow exponentially in the next years.  👨‍💼 Middle Class Historically, the global real estate investment market has only been available to a small subset of investors. This is not fair, and Alt.Estate will provide unprecedented access to the global real estate market for most of the population, who could not participate in this economy before.  📈 Traders Alt.Estate makes no recommendations about any particular investment, but the Platform provides investors with tools, relevant information, market data, sponsor information, property information and third-party information.  🐋 Crypto Whales Many early Bitcoin and Ether miners and investors have made a fortune. In addition to the motivation of all crypto investors to reduce exposure to crypto assets and diversify their portfolio, they need a convenient and low-cost way to buy expensive real assets.  💰 Institutional Investors Institutional investors increase their deal flow through virtually outsourcing part of their job to find lucrative real estate investment opportunities to Alt.Estate. Also, institutions can earn a higher return through negotiating special investment terms for being cornerstone investors providing a substantial part of the fundraising amount.

Author: Alt.Estate
Title: [ANN] Alt.Estate — Trade Tokenized Real Estate! USA, Japan, EU... [BOUNTYHIVE]
Body: We’re sure, that our project is weidhty and innovative enough to achieve our goals. We offer real estate market players our Protocol for real estate tokenization, and the Platform for exchanging tokenized real estate assets. Tokenization enables trading real estate in small fractions, and makes it accessible as a result. Sellers attract new buyers who could not afford to buy real estate before, didn’t have the opportunity to invest internationally, didn’t want to bear high transaction costs, or wanted to pay for real estate with cryptocurrency. Buyers are additionally motivated by the transparency and liquidity provided by the secondary market within the Platform and the secure transaction records stored on the blockchain.  Alt.Estate makes it possible to buy and sell tokenized real estate assets in a trusted, fast and smooth manner with instantaneous transactions and low transaction costs. Any real estate owner can list his property or any fraction of it on the Platform, and anyone can become a buyer as the entry ticket is very low.  We are the first real estate tokenization project with a viable B2B marketing strategy. We will provide our solution to real estate developers, investment companies and brokers. As they are interested in any new sales channels, we can use their marketing budgets to promote our tokenization Protocol and quickly fill our exchange with tokenized real estate from all over the world.

Title: [ANN] Alt.Estate — Trade Tokenized Real Estate! USA, Japan, EU... [BOUNTYHIVE]
Body: 🏘 The Blockchain For Real Estate, Explained 🏘  🤔 Like the original internet, the blockchain is a revolution in technology that will touch all people and all businesses. So people are paying attention, but many still don’t understand what the blockchain is.   🚀 In its most simple sense, the blockchain is a series of computers (thousands to potentially millions of them) that each keep the same record of an event or transaction in a ledger that is open to the public. Each record is encrypted, and the ledger is virtually hack-proof.  👨‍💼 Bitcoin is merely an application of the blockchain. When people buy homes with bitcoin, they really are still buying with cash. It’s just being converted to bitcoin first.  📌 Note: Alt.Estate uses blockchain technologies to disrupt the real estate market. We have a strong potential to become an industry standard for the blockchain-based real estate transactions.  👉 Read more interesting facts here: https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbesrealestatecouncil/2018/04/23/the-blockchain-for-real-estate-explained/#30b085ae781e  🔥 Don't forget that we have launched the Alt.Estate Platform MVP and limited presale. Author: Alt.Estate
Title: [ANN] Alt.Estate — Trade Tokenized Real Estate! USA, Japan, EU... [BOUNTYHIVE]
Body: MVP stands for Minimum Viable Product. MVP is a stage of the product, that includes the proof that it solves a real problem for users, so that they are actually finding benefit in adopting the product.  Alt.Estate Protocol is based on the two-layer token model. ALT and SQM Tokens.  SQM tokens are property-specific tokens, which are created when a new property is tokenized. Each property listed on the Platform has its own SQM.  ALT token is the internal currency of the Platform and the fuel of the Protocol. The ALT token is a pure utility token used for several important functions within the Platform. ALT token price can fluctuate substantially.

Title: [ANN] Alt.Estate — Trade Tokenized Real Estate! USA, Japan, EU... [BOUNTYHIVE]
Body: Alt.Estate  Advantages  Low Entry Ticket  The ability to buy a 1/1,000 fraction of a property makes it accessible to anyone.   Low Transaction Costs  Traditional costs of up to 30% of property price are eliminated with tokenization.   Global Portfolio  Individuals and institutions can buy or sell fractions of properties without borders.   Strong Expertise  The Alt.Estate team and advisors have more than $4bn worth of transaction experience in real estate. The diverse team background and expertise inspire breakthrough innovation.   Investment Portfolio  Even a small investor can diversify his portfolio by purchasing tokens of a Manhattan penthouse, a warehouse in Guangzhou, a coworking space in Amsterdam and villas in Bali.   Security & Protection  Due diligence procedures prior to the property token offering and distributed storage of all the collected information provide additional protection.

Author: yuvadeep
Title: [ANN] Alt.Estate — Trade Tokenized Real Estate! USA, Japan, EU... [BOUNTYHIVE]
Body: In 2015, the total economic value of the World real estate went around $ 217 trillion and the amount successfully brings about 2.7 times that is of global GDP. All these can be involved only in the developed real estate. Thus, undeveloped large area around the globe is not yet calculated. Real estate market brings many offers that help them in bringing profits; it is easier to invest in stocks and bonds rather than investing in real estate because they face many problems in real estate Some of the problems faced by the investors in the real estate markets are given below •   Transaction cost is very high in purchasing the real estate. •   Insufficient funds for paying bills or repaying loans •   The process will be very slow and complications occur in changing their own name and address in real estate •   Not having the clear knowledge about the price •   Fraud can be done in real property transactions •   Difficulties in doing transactions for both domestic trade and international trade All these problems occur many times, and to solve some of the problems they came up with the best solution to invest in new vehicles. But there is no perfect solution and real estate still facing many problems Real estate tokenization is one of the best methods on the blockchain technology helps to solve the problems of real estate investments in a natural way. All the transactions are registered in a single public blockchain, that helps them to eliminate fraud and availability of the cash and clear picture of the price by converting into digital cash helps to exchange.  By taking the help of property tokens, users can trade that can easily use or understand.
